{"tid":1470273,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"經過琴日之後決定唔再去機場嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-14T06:56:03.000Z","uid":33143,"like":6,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"cfe237353243031066793e650fb49bbdb3b89c57","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:44:01.000Z","msg":"我剩係問一句<br />\n你班仆街知唔知自己係為d乜入機場?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講撚左好多次 佔機場係為左通過斷絕旅客上落機 <br />\n用壓力迫政府讓步 而唔係坐埋一邊係到舉牌文宣但又比旅客順利上落機呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我實在唔明點解個個都天真到以為靠舉牌嗌口號說服外國人<br />\n佢地就會幫你同港共施壓?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n大佬 人地又唔係香港人 幫你有咩益處?<br />\n將心比己 你去其他國家見到呢啲情況你又會幫佢地做野咩?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話佔機場阻人上落機會搞到旅客好嬲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 影響民意 <br />\nOK 你岩 呢個冇人要反對 <br />\n又將心比己 你係外國玩完返黎但點撚知係機場比人擋路搞到要delay 你都一樣嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你話咁樣咪即係囉旅客做人質迫政府投降 <br />\n呢個比喻我都唔會反對 但我希望你地面對現實 <br />\n呢個世界冇一個抗爭運動係完全唔會影響局外人 冇一個抗爭運動係可以用0成本達成目的<br />\n 冇一個抗爭運動係可以拎足100分 因為點都有人會因為我地出黎而受影響<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而且都會消耗我地一定體力<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又會有機會比狗拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">但係如果你達成唔到目的 唔理你用咩方法 你都係得0分 </span></span></span><br />\n如果你睇完仲係堅持舉牌嗌口號就可以說服旅客幫你同港共施壓 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我唔阻止你 你可以繼續做<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但希望你地唔好再屌人擋路搞到旅客行唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">最後我要警告 <br />\n如果呢場係因為你班仆街屌到冇人願意塞機場嘅話 <br />\n我可以肯定呢幾日嘅成效會係0 <br />\n你浪費左幾萬人哂時間哂車費黎爭取大家想要嘅目標 <br />\n呢場抗爭運動失敗嘅話你地絕對責無旁貸</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8af0014aee2994f8470f04fb79fd69cc43a9f9f1","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:51:56.000Z","msg":"自推呀屌"},{"pid":"46f5f6d56a1d4f3dfb65b0eba19f47aa62ffad29","tid":1470273,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:52:17.000Z","msg":"【重要通知】抗爭不割蓆手冊<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470153\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470153</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n請參閱"},{"pid":"6d813cc6c95358ab049c0449b54dd524be8634ac","tid":1470273,"uid":60773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:53:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b545de2d83b950f780ba4fd93df234a0eb36b1f5","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:56:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d133b552400f65e402a80b4c25909b776abd36b","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:59:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79756b41289f769d6d7ba1251470435d6cd05b7a","tid":1470273,"uid":37894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:59:27.000Z","msg":"我地應該每星期搵一日，同一個時間一齊搭車入機場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1468945\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1468945</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"15f7df9302a33864292cff81254bbbd218936f9c","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T04:59:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62152a43cc1d113d751b572e2fd73880c3789d3c","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:01:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfcab330d3b578c7a611dd20978a0ce29f738b82","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:02:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068402d211ea1005efe391c32c0e9b9aa3542597","tid":1470273,"uid":33143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T05:05:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1c9505f646ff26c7043f897a54ea217f261d64e","tid":1470273,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:37:36.000Z","msg":"我buy陳雲<br />\n呢段時間唔需要示威者主動添加壓力<br />\n由國際做野<br />\n香港人只需和理非keep住溫度<br />\n<br />\n我上過前塞過錢塞過紅隧<br />\n但會過埋呢一水<br />\n睇下國際做唔做到野先做和理非以外嘅野"},{"pid":"b9af9465c7baf7d62a553d403ccda096ecc792b6","tid":1470273,"uid":233839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:42:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: navy;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">大家不斷屌主動塞機場<br />\n812做完 813唔堅持做的話 去展示大家嘅決心<br />\n我最怕係下次要做到8全民塞爆機場係等要死人嘅時侯<br />\n明白未？</span></span>"},{"pid":"4922760a47fd75cfe27ed1684c293ade6adfc770","tid":1470273,"uid":281904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:45:00.000Z","msg":"香港人，召集，818大遊行見"},{"pid":"965779c2436fe8efce51cbd1c3a91f9e33ca9297","tid":1470273,"uid":83477,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T06:56:03.000Z","msg":"癱瘓機場<br />\n變左鳩叫口號 派傳單<br />\n<br />\n人唔笑狗都笑<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}